x.php?options=content&id=587|title=Az\u0259rbaycan Respublikas\u0131n\u0131n Xarici \u0130\u015fl\u0259r Nazirliyi Az\u0259rbaycan Respublikas\u0131n\u0131n v\u0259t\u0259nda\u015flar\u0131na  Liviyada m\u00f6vcud olan v\u0259ziyy\u0259tl\u0259 ba\u011fl\u0131 x\u0259b\u0259rdarl\u0131q edir, 12 may 2011-ci il.|first=|last=FS|publisher=}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Russia}} [[Russian closed city|Closed cities]] of [[Russia]]\n| {{yes-no|Special authorization required}}\n|\n| Several [[Russian closed city|closed cities and regions in Russia]] require special authorization.<ref name=\"Russia\"/>\n|-\n| {{flag|South Ossetia}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}\n|\n| Multiple entry visa to [[Russia]] and three-day prior notification are required to enter South Ossetia.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mfa-rso.su/node/55|title=\u041e \u0432\u0438\u0437\u0430\u0445 - \u041c\u0438\u043d\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u0438\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0445 \u0434\u0435\u043b|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mfa-rso.su/en/node/406|title=Procedure of the Entry to the Territory of the Republic of South Ossetia - \u041c\u0438\u043d\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u0438\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0445 \u0434\u0435\u043b|access-date=2013-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015140424/http://www.mfa-rso.su/en/node/406|archive-date=2013-10-15|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Svalbard}}\n| {{free|Visa not required}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Visa and passport requirements|url=http://www.spitsbergen-svalbard.com/2011/10/05/visa-and-passport-requirements.html|accessdate= 19 March 2015}}</ref>\n| Unlimited \n| [[Svalbard Treaty]]\n|-\n| {{flag|Transnistria}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}\n| {{ntsh|1}}24 hours\n| Registration required after 24h.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.luxlana.net/Transdniestr.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2015-08-04 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=